Introduction

Ten is a Thai singer under SM Entertainment. He is a member of the boy group NCT and its sub-units NCT U and WayV. He is formerly a member of the pre-debut team SM Rookies.

On October 4th, 2019, he debuted once more under SM Entertainment's supergroup, SuperM.
